text: ADVICE IF YOU EVER FEEL SUICIDALOkay  so  when I was about    currently   I was diagnosed with depression  anxiety  ADD  amp  many more disorders  I felt insane  so different  I couldn t handle it  It became to the point where I would wait for my mom to sleep so I can cut myself without getting caught  one day  we got into this huge argument over something stupid  amp  I was so much more heart broken that I ran out of my house and I went to the closest abandoned grain elevator  amp  I made my way to the roof  I walked to the edge  stood on the peak  was about to jump before I realized I had a dog that saw me leave  amp  would be devastated if I never came home  So instead I chose to text a random number  just put in a bunch of numbers and to my surprise  I got an answer  I texted  idk if anyone is ever going to answer but I m going to kill myself in   minutes  the number texted back almost instantly saying  please don t  I know what you re going through may be extremely tough but just because you end YOUR pain doesn t mean you re not passing it to someone else  and so I took the opportunity to ball my eyes out and talk about EVERYTHING  To this day  he s my bestfriend  my life  my lover and my whole entire reason I m still here  don t ever give up  you re more than welcome to text me  I don t ever want you to think that suicide is the only option  When I went back home  my mom had the police there and everything  just seeing her crying that hard and begging for me to come home really gave me a different perspective in life  Value what you have
